%p
  The first stop of today is the Summer Palace.
  As today is a saturday, it is a little bit busier the normal.

= photo(:src => '//cdn.matsimitsu.com/asia2014/day-three/day-two-1.jpg', :width => '1100', :height => '729')
= photo(:src => '//cdn.matsimitsu.com/asia2014/day-three/day-two-3.jpg', :width => '1100', :height => '729')
%p
  As with every monument you can buy an pass to enter the park, but that doesn't mean you can enter everything in the park. To do that you need to buy an all-acces pass. With this we were able to walk down here by the water, yay!

