%p Being Dutch as we are we decided to not spend the 3 Yuan on a bike ride to the subway station and walk over there ourselves. After a couple of minutes we figured out we were heading the wrong way. It took us a good 15 minutes to get to the subway station. 3 Yuan is not even 40 euro cents...

= photo(:src => '//cdn.matsimitsu.com/asia2014/day-three/day-two-25.jpg', :width => '1100', :height => '729')
